de: Supplemental Contribution Amendment to the Administration Agreement between the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research of Switzerland, acting through its State Secretariat for Economic Affairs, and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Debt Management Facility Phase II (DMF II) Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072132)  - 06-01-2015 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO und der International Bank for Reconstruction and Development (IBRD) betreffend des Schweizer Beitrags für die zweite Phase der Debt Management Facility (DMF)
en: Supplemental Contribution Amendment to the Administration Agreement between the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research of Switzerland, acting through its State Secretariat for Economic Affairs, and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Debt Management Facility Phase II (DMF II) Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072132)  - 06-01-2015 - Administration Agreement between the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research of Switzerland, acting through its State Secretariat for Economic Affairs, and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Debt Management Facility Phase II (DMF II) Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072132)
fr: Supplemental Contribution Amendment to the Administration Agreement between the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research of Switzerland, acting through its State Secretariat for Economic Affairs, and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Debt Management Facility Phase II (DMF II) Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072132)  - 06-01-2015 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et la Banque internationale pour la reconstruction et le développement (BIRD) concernant la contribution suisse pour la deuxième phase de la Debt Management Facility (DMF)
